# Harness Airgap Bundle Selection File
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Use with: ./download-airgap-bundles.sh --version <ver> --output-dir ./bundles \
#               --selection-file selection.conf
#
# Tip: run --generate-selection-file to build this file interactively, or
#      run --list to see all available names.
# Lines starting with '#' are ignored.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# List of bundles to download (comma-separated).
# This includes Modules, Plugins, Agents, and Scanners.
#
# - Modules (e.g. platform, ci): Dependencies are auto-resolved.
# - Plugins (e.g. ci-plugins): Must be listed explicitly if needed.
# - Agents (e.g. delegate, upgrader): Must be listed explicitly.
# - Scanners (e.g. grype-job-runner): Must be listed explicitly.
#
# Use 'all' to download everything available in the manifest.
#
# Example: bundles=platform,ci,ci-plugins,delegate,delegate-fips
bundles=
